YORK CITY IS COMPLICATED.

00:01:49.475 --> 00:01:53.045 align:start size:91% position:9% line:91%
JUST ASK ARCHITECT ENRIQUE
NORTON.

00:01:53.078 --> 00:01:55.882 align:start size:97% position:3% line:91%
