CITY. 

00:01:55.915 --> 00:01:58.151 line:91%
BUT OBVIOUSLY, YOU KNOW, A LOT
OF THINGS GET BUILT HERE AND A

00:01:58.184 --> 00:02:01.387 align:start size:94% position:6% line:91%
